HEADWORD: Poundcake
<hw>Pound"cake`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of rich,
sweet cake; -- so called from the ingredients being used by pounds, or
in equal quantities.</def>⟦br⟧
